save their life

00:41:55.440 --> 00:42:00.240
or add additional happy
healthy years to their life,

00:42:00.240 --> 00:42:03.160
would you share that
information with them?

00:42:03.160 --> 00:42:05.440
Of course, you would.

00:42:05.440 --> 00:42:09.110
So that brings me to
my next question--

00:42:09.110 --> 00:42:12.530
