your loved ones?

00:42:17.930 --> 00:42:23.060
Because in reality,
we have two homes.

00:42:23.060 --> 00:42:25.910
We have our body, and
we have our planet.

00:42:25.910 --> 00:42:28.790
And it's imperative that we
take care of both of them.

